					section.count__button
						p#count__button_copy Click to say #metoo.
						
						p#count__button_after_click The bigger the number the harder it is to ignore.
				
					section.count__copy
						p We can't even begin to count how many of our friends, family members, colleagues, girls-met-in-nightclub-toilets, school lollipop ladies, or mum's mates have said #metoo. It's a damn shame. Even us women had no idea the problem was this huge. But it's huge.<br />HUGE. 

						p The problem is, the #metoo hashtag only gives a voice to those who feel comfortable using it. We want to give everyone a chance to say #metoo, anonymously. And we don't want it to get lost in your newsfeed.

						p Facts can change behaviour.<br />So help us put this monster of a number in one place. <strong>Click the button above</strong> to be counted as a human being that has been sexually harassed or assaulted.
						
